s/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係完左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c29bf78b6ee82468acfd6f25511cdfa859afba","tid":322200,"uid":11397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"ee20f71ff93847e359f8318b4d5453679e6022be","tid":322200,"uid":11397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:28:45.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"1927d0a61c8bfa4760ecde1766c8145d0e1df494","tid":322200,"uid":11397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"f0d9e5d1824b8ee8b02daf02acd4e39a2ec2b9bd","tid":322200,"uid":11397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"93d2bebee5f8c9ef7a3dc2e6c47bb46b475a1cdf","tid":322200,"uid":11397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"六，快d搵人救我"},{"pid":"d8386dee604b602aecdff5e6c1ee2c56a622001b","tid":322200,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六，快d搵人救我</blockquote><br />\nk"},{"pid":"cf180ba1179fea9b4c01a445549f3f5a17dce360","tid":322200,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T17:46:50.000Z","msg":"雅各不時別過頭來問我在想什麼，而我只會搖搖頭説沒有什麼。直到現在我還是覺得一切都很不真實，如果這是夢，我希望它是個永遠不會醒來的夢。就在我出神的期間，我們早已到達目的地。我跟隨雅各進入巫師登記處，這裡和我想像中的很不同，我原以為氣氛會是嚴肅而又莊重，但這裡人聲鼎沸有無數的人進出，而你可以一眼就能辨認出那些是「初生兒」。他們的神情都帶點慌張小心翼翼的跟在巫師後面，時而四處張望，時而低下頭來。就在一瞬間，我和一個男孩對上眼來，他和別的人不同，他神色自若而又帶幾分自信。<br />\n<br />\n就這麼一瞬間，我知道他是與眾不同的。回過神來雅各手中握便著一張薄紙，微微泛黃的薄紙上印有我的姓名甚至出生日期和相片。最令我驚訝的是紙上竟印有我的相片，而在相片底下則印著號碼&mdash;2036。雅各揮手示意叫我跟隨他，我隨著雅各走上櫃位前，所謂的巫師登記處也真夠寬敞，大概有百多個櫃位並列排著，人流絡繹不絕，不消三兩下就有新巫師的誔生。令人為之概嘆的是隨了其寬大的空間，更是其設計，這𥚃都統一用上棗紅的實木門窗，在大堂的上方懸掛著時間儀，而時間儀是實木雕刻配上巫師仗作為分針和秒針。配上鵝黃的燈光映照下這裡帶點神秘之餘又有幾分詭秘的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n櫃台職員大抵是早已厭倦其重複的工作，他瞬間就從雅各手上取過薄紙來，他只用了三秒檢查紙張便抬起頭來看我的容貌，突如其來的注視使我有點緊張，雅各看出我的緊張便拍拍我的肩膀，奇怪的是我的確放鬆起來。"},{"pid":"5af12e08923e97ece3db1b1432c4c85c39736155","tid":322200,"uid":26956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:27:32.000Z","msg":"今日先諗緊幾時有會文，點知真係有文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff4db6ce0fde87a51bad1aa6f59867e2c293442","tid":322200,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:35:32.000Z","msg":"文！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e9bd2fb2253135213bcb3975e0e028f9cf0251","tid":322200,"uid":25613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T19:57:58.000Z","msg":"我已經唔記得之前講到去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9f6832eec15b53ceaec959652aceae9e2df268","tid":322200,"uid":1